    public class NeoEContentsEList<E>
extends EContentsEList<E>
implements EList<E>, InternalEList<E>
    An EContentsEList implementation that delegates its operations to the associated PersistentStore.

    Instances of this class are created by Resource.getContents() and allows to access the content of a PersistentResource by lazily loading the elements.
